BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:tPfTU8A32g5a6sP9SmWmM
SUMMARY:Maple Arts Sing Along
DTSTAMP:20260306T013338Z
DTSTART:20260328T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Whoome is excited to bring Sing Along to Seattle for the first 
	time. An unforgettable musical experience! \\nThis one-of-a-kind event inv
	ites you to take center stage\\\, singing timeless Arabic classics chosen 
	by you\\\, our audience. With digital lyrics provided\\\, everyone gets to
	 be the lead singer in this interactive musical celebration. \\nJoin Maple
	 Arts Group in Seattle for an evening filled with joy\\\, connection\\\, a
	nd the magic of music. Don’t miss your chance to be part of this extraordi
	nary sing-along experience! \\nThe evening will be presented by Maple Arts
	 Group musicians from the Canadian Arabic Orchestra. \\n\\nEvents are offe
	red for informational\\\, entertainment\\\, and educational purposes only.
	 Read Town Hall’s Program Content Policy.\n\nhttps://townhallseattle.org/e
	vent/maple-arts-sing-along/\n\nFrom Town Hall Seattle
URL:https://townhallseattle.org/event/maple-arts-sing-along/
LOCATION:The Great Hall\\\, 1119 Eighth Avenue (enter on Eighth Avenue)\\\,
	 Seattle\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:town-hall-seattle
CATEGORIES:Town Hall Seattle
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT
